      <PointerOffset>40808</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_177_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;、たまにはお肉とかお魚料理以外も
食べたいのに</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, &lt;Dio&gt;, I wanna eat something other than meat
or fish.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40880</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_177_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレは肉が食いたいの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But I only want to eat meat dishes!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_177_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>好き嫌いは体によくないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, being picky isn't good for your body.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41024</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_177_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もうお肉飽きた！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ugh, I'm already sick of meat!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41156</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_177_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お肉ばっか食べてる&lt;Dio&gt;なんて、ハゲワシか
イソギンチャクになっちゃえばいいんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You always eat meat, &lt;Dio&gt;! It'd be better if
you were a vulture or an anemone!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41220</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_177_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんないって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Nah, that'd never happen!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
